Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:19.87,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be2}ワガママMirror heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:24.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be2}逆さまに純情揺れて
