Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\c&H716E6A&\bord0\fs45\frz10.14\pos(1230.399,585.6)}第一名    壁咚!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  政宗君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你在聽嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,能拜託你認真討論嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz270\fsp15\bord0\b0\pos(1793.601,385.301)\c&HF1F1EE&}八坂祭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs52.5\fsp15\bord0\b0\frz272.8\pos(1284.803,575.702)\c&HF1F1EE&}班級節目會議
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  班長…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好好想想班上出什麼節目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,節目啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好好  不才雙葉妙  絞盡腦汁想了個主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,讓超級可愛的小十娘演白雪公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,讓超級帥氣的政宗君演白馬王子的戲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那可真妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…為什麼我演公主?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,加油  二年B班!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放棄吧  小十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒人能反抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,到頭來還是會這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\c&HA45753&\bord0\fs42\frz314.5\pos(1158.401,269.699)}心跳特輯!!
